    [ctns_front]
Field Axioms<br/><br/>Closure Under Addition
    [/ctns_front]

    [ctns_frontspeak]
Field Axioms -- -- Closure Under Addition
    [/ctns_frontspeak]

    [ctns_back style='width:80%;']
A set $$\mathbb{F}$$ is <strong>closed under addition</strong> for all values $$x, y \in \mathbb{F}$$
<br/><br/>if $$x+y \in \mathbb{F}$$ and $$x+y$$ is unique.
    [/ctns_back]

    [ctns_backspeak]
A set F is closed under addition for all values x and y in F if the sum of x plus y is both unique and a member of F
    [/ctns_backspeak]

[/ctns_make]
